      "rationale": "Power-law hemolysis model output (normalized index of hemolysis, NIH) is the accepted clinical surrogate. Conversion to plasma-free hemoglobin is documented but carries ±25% uncertainty from model form. QoI is relevant but conversion uncertainty is large. Gradation 3 achieved; 4 required."
    },
