      "rationale": "FDA generic pump geometry differs from patient-specific VAD impeller design. Rotational speeds used in validation (2000–3500 RPM) partially overlap VAD COU range (2500–4500 RPM). Geometric similarity is insufficient for absolute hemolysis prediction. Gradation 2 achieved; 4 required."
    },
