      "acceptanceCriteria": "Alternative hemolysis models (Giersiepen, Taskin, modified power-law) must be evaluated; model form uncertainty must be quantified and bounded.",
      "rationale": "Only Giersiepen power-law model used. Alternative model forms not evaluated. Model form uncertainty not quantified. The UQ campaign addressed parametric uncertainty within the chosen model form only; inter-model variability not explored. Gradation 1 default; 4 required."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
