      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary conditions must have documented uncertainty distributions; Monte Carlo propagation must cover full input space.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ campaign (n=2000) propagated uncertainty in inlet velocity profile and blood viscosity. Shear-stress model coefficient uncertainty was identified as dominant by the UQ campaign but was not included in the propagation as an input variable. Input uncertainty coverage incomplete. Gradation 2 achieved; 4 required."
