      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum 5 independent experimental replicates per operating point with documented inter-sample variability.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark dataset provides 3 replicates at 3 of 5 operating points; 2 operating points have single measurements. Inter-sample variability not formally characterized. Test sample factor not assessed at required depth. Gradation 1 default; 3 required."
