      "rationale": "Equivalency mapping between experimental and computational inlet conditions not formally documented. Rotational speed tolerance ±50 RPM not verified in simulation setup. Factor not assessed; flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Gradation 1 default; 3 required."
